<h2>Competitive Advantages</h2>
<ul> 
	<li>IPG’s Global Market Entry Partnership uses an equity and profit sharing based model rather than fee based. There is little up-front costs to clients. If IPG does not do a best job or provide the most accurate advice, it would not make any profit. As a result, IPG’s interests are almost perfectly aligned with its clients.</li>
	<li>IPG is not a technology firm and do not wish to steal the partner’s IP or manage partner’s firm for forever. Partner firms will gain control of their Chinese company once it’s operating smoothly. </li>
	<li>Most IPG people are Chinese expatriates with extensive experience in both China and aboard. They are better communicators who understand both east and west. IPG people are young, passionate, ethical, and flexible. </li>
	<li>China is arguably the most promising market going forward.</li>
</ul>